    "levelAdaptation": "<div><p>After level 5: +5 Health, +D4 damage, +10 Combat Skill</p></div><div><p>After level 10: +5 Health, +D6 damage, +10 Combat Skill</p></div>",
    "actions": [
      {
        "startDie": 1,
        "endDie": 2,
        "name": "Constricting Grasp (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Cavebound Leech lunges at a target, attempting to wrap its slimy body around them and constrict. It makes a melee attack, dealing D6 Bludgeoning damage on a hit. If the attack hits, the target is Restrained. The target takes 1 Bludgeoning damage at the start of each of their turns while Restrained. The Cavebound Leech doesn't act against a character while they are affected by this Action; instead, it uses its Engulfing Devour Action.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Razor Bite (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Cavebound Leech strikes with its razor-sharp teeth, attempting to pierce the target's flesh. It makes a melee attack, dealing D6 Piercing damage on a hit. This attack ignores all Armor.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 5,
        "endDie": 6,
        "name": "Engulfing Devour (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Cavebound Leech targets a creature it has Restrained with its Constricting Grasp ability. It opens its maw wide and attempts to engulf the creature, dealing 2D8 Acid damage. If no creature was affected by Constricting Grasp, the Cavebound Leech deals D6 Piercing damage, healing for half of the damage done.</p></div>"
      }
    ],
    "description": "<div><p>The slimy, segmented body of a Cavebound Leech stretches for several meters, with a glistening, mucus-covered exoskeleton that allows it to move effortlessly through the underground passages. Its elongated, razor-sharp teeth line its maw, capable of piercing through even the sturdiest of armors. The Cavebound Leech lies in wait for its prey and ready to strike with lightning speed to devour them with its terrible jaws.</p></div>",
